hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583195fa141dbdda6c0b988c6212f7891fd37657","tid":52971,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T01:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依個時候就會有葡萄撚話支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公平講<br />\n支那同葡萄係兩回事"},{"pid":"7f0ef615754181b3c71e0c1d4136e96351b35bad","tid":52971,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:01:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用個仔個名買有首次置業 唔洗交印花稅？<br />\n之後轉番落老豆名？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉名要比番錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明眼人一睇就知係避左個稅啦<br />\n唔好講到對個仔有幾好<br />\n<br />\n不過豪宅租值回報率好抵"},{"pid":"504429821417817bdca85589bc21adac5aba5213","tid":52971,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7258ad3a72d5a07e6a0bed50dd6b069cda6fc93b","tid":52971,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用個仔個名買有首次置業 唔洗交印花稅？<br />\n之後轉番落老豆名？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉名要比番錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明眼人一睇就知係避左個稅啦<br />\n唔好講到對個仔有幾好<br />\n<br />\n不過豪宅租值回報率好抵</blockquote><br />\n明眼人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇幾句野就知人諗乜"},{"pid":"9a9ff4bba218b7a91e02eb7ee9960494375cdd16","tid":52971,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:34:14.000Z","msg":"呢隻先叫贏在起跑線呀，讀埋啲咩精英班呀，用假地址報名校果班家長，收皮啦你地"},{"pid":"c2ce3bebf2f1a18882dcf117507efad028aa8e16","tid":52971,"uid":23769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:18:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c96a184906c894e4e53305df778072a443bd1c0d","tid":52971,"uid":23769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"959a51fc753